UMFPACK
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
UMFPACK, Copyright (c) 2005-2023, Timothy A. Davis. All Rights Reserved.
License: GPL-2.0-or-later.
Availability: http://www.suitesparse.com
Used by permission.

The supernodal multifrontal LU kernel in src/multifrontal.jl (and the symbolic
analysis feeding it in src/symbolic.jl) implements UMFPACK's algorithm, and the
factorization conventions exposed in src/scaling.jl, src/solve.jl, and
src/interface.jl follow UMFPACK's semantics (row scaling, the
(Rs .* A)[p, q] == L * U convention). Because UMFPACK is GPL-2.0-or-later, the
combined distributed work must be GPL-2.0-or-later; it cannot be relicensed under
a permissive license such as MIT.

