CSparse
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CSparse: a Concise Sparse matrix package.
Copyright (c) 2006, Timothy A. Davis.
License: LGPL-2.1-or-later.
Availability: http://www.suitesparse.com

src/amd.jl is a faithful port of CSparse cs_amd; src/symbolic.jl ports
cs_etree / cs_post / cs_tdfs; colamd_order follows CSparse cs_amd(order = 2)
(AMD on the A'A column-intersection graph with dense rows dropped -- this is the
cs_amd order=2 construction, not Davis's separate standalone COLAMD library); and
the Gilbert-Peierls LU kernel in src/gplu.jl follows CSparse cs_lu.

